### Create your first Channel

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/realtime/getting_started.mdx

Examples for creating a Realtime channel with a descriptive topic name, including private channel configuration.

```ts
// Create a channel with a descriptive topic name
const channel = supabase.channel('room:lobby:messages', {
  config: { private: true }, // Recommended for production
})
```

```dart
// Create a channel with a descriptive topic name
final channel = supabase.channel('room:lobby:messages');
```

```swift
// Create a channel with a descriptive topic name
let channel = supabase.channel("room:lobby:messages") {
  $0.isPrivate = true
}
```

