### Multiplatform Ktor Client Engine example

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/docs/ref/kotlin/installing.mdx

Example of adding Ktor Client Engine dependencies for different Kotlin multiplatform targets.

```kotlin
commonMain {
    dependencies {
        //Supabase modules
    }
}
jvmMain {
    dependencies {
        implementation("io.ktor:ktor-client-cio:KTOR_VERSION")
    }
}
androidMain {
    dependsOn(jvmMain.get())
}
